articles.title: What we learned from Friday practice for F1's Saudi Arabian GP - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Despite suffering from a stomach bug, reigning champion Max Verstappen was in imperious form after Friday's running ahead of the Formula 1 Saudi Arabian Grand Prix. But behind, any one of a number of teams could be best of the rest
articles.content:
Max Verstappen delivered another hammer blow to his rivals hopes of challenging Red Bull after his clean sweep of Friday practice sessions ahead of Formula 1s Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.
